 If you remember. 

00:02:15.299 --> 00:02:16.309
 The water is, of course, 

00:02:17.309 --> 00:02:19.109
 the most important raw material 

00:02:19.109 --> 00:02:21.429
 that we have today, in the world. 

00:02:22.429 --> 00:02:25.299
 It's a question of whether we should privatize 

00:02:25.299 --> 00:02:29.969
 the normal supply of water to the population. 

00:02:29.969 --> 00:02:32.829
 and there are 2 different opinions on this issue. 

00:02:32.829 --> 00:02:36.769
 One of them, which I think is extreme 

00:02:36.769 --> 00:02:39.999
 is represented by NGOs 

00:02:39.999 --> 00:02:42.289
 that hammer on 

00:02:42.289 --> 00:02:45.389
 declare water 

00:02:47.409 --> 00:02:50.000
 a public right. 

