 It means that, as a human being, you should have the right to 

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:56.669
 the water. 

00:02:56.669 --> 00:02:59.609
 This is an extreme solution. 

00:02:59.609 --> 00:03:03.469
 And another view is that 

00:03:02.469 --> 00:03:06.639
 water is a food like any other. 

00:03:06.939 --> 00:03:12.289
 and, like any other food, should have a market value. 

00:03:12.289 --> 00:03:14.749
 Personally, I think it's better ... 

00:03:14.749 --> 00:03:17.540
 price a food 

00:03:17.540 --> 00:03:23.000
 so that we are all aware of its price 

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:28.000
 and then take specific measures ... 

00:03:28.349 --> 00:03:32.889
 for the part of the population that has no access to this water 

00:03:32.889 --> 00:03:36.139
 having many different possibilities there. 

00:03:43.669 --> 00:03:46.009
 I still think that ... 

00:03:46.009 --> 00:03:48.929
 the greater social responsibility ... 

00:03:48.929 --> 00:03:52.559
 of any Director is ... 

00:03:52.559 --> 00:03:54.779
 maintain and secure a future 

00:03:54.779 --> 00:04:01.029
 profitable and successful business. 

